OL,6,FThe Horizon IT scandal saw more than
OL,7,F700 sub-postmasters prosecuted by the
OL,8,FPost Office and handed criminal
OL,9,Fconvictions between 1999 and 2015 as
OL,10,FFujitsu's faulty system made it appear
OL,11,Fas though money was missing at their
OL,12,Fbranches.
OL,14,FHundreds of sub-postmasters are still
OL,15,Fawaiting compensation despite the
OL,16,FGovernment announcing those who have
OL,17,Fhad convictions quashed are eligible
OL,18,Ffor #600,000 payouts.
